1412
01:41:32,092 --> 01:41:33,844
Nunca mais me chame de Django.

1413
01:41:36,722 --> 01:41:38,682
Me perdoe.

1414
01:41:42,311 --> 01:41:43,937
- Venham aqui, pessoal.
- Pessoal?

1415
01:41:44,313 --> 01:41:46,106
